flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic planning run or detection of critical component shortage (from SAP S/4HANA) that threatens committed production schedules or OTD targets.]
  A --> N1[Stream: STREAMS - Ingest and normalize transactional and master data from SAP S/4HANA and supplier feeds into the DI subject area]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex RCA Service - Detect shortage and identify candidate bottlenecks + contributors using pattern mining]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Process Builder (Data Science / Remote Functions) - Simulate mitigation scenarios (alternate suppliers, cross-plant shifts, expedited logistics) and evaluate cost vs. service trade-offs]
  N3 --> N4{PB: Agent Team - Agentic decisioning composes prioritized action plan and triggers approvals where needed}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Process Builder - Execute coordinated actions (ERP writebacks, scheduling changes, PO updates, logistics priorities) and create CWB items for exceptions]
  N5 --> N6[PB: UI Screen - Surface outcomes and KPIs (COGS delta, OTD impact, execution audit) to operations and finance]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced stockouts and line-stops, improved OTD for affected orders, measurable P&L impact (lower emergency procurement premium vs. lost revenue), and an auditable decision trail of simulated scenarios, selected mitigations, and execution outcomes.]
  N4 -->|Preferred supplier cannot expedite or...| B1[Agentic flow selects next-best supplier or triggers quality-weighted supplier qualification and re-evaluates routing/production mitigations]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Mitigation executed with higher procurement cost and validated supplier; production impact minimized but COGS increases]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Cross-plant capacity insufficient to ...| B2[Escalate to C-level via CWB Lifecycle with proposed overtime/subcontracting costs or customer re-phasing options]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Human-approved exception increases cost but restores throughput or triggers controlled order delivery adjustments]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Source data is incomplete or stale (q...| B3[Hold automated execution, flag data owners, and run conservative fallback plan (use last-known safe buffers); notify stakeholders]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Reduced automation; conservative actions protect service but may increase temporary inventory/cost]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]